on ubunutu:
sudo apt-get install libgdal20 libgdal-dev python3-gdal

in a virtual env or on centos7 (meade03):
install gdal and the gdal-dev libraries globally (on centos7 use yumdownloader --resolve gdal gdal-devel)

make sure the python gdal version and library/binary versions match
https://gist.github.com/cspanring/5680334

pip download gdal=1.11.2
tar -xvf ...
cd ...
python setup.py build_ext --include-dirs=/home/tthompson/tools/usr/include/gdal
